snippet.title: Skyward Battles (Playdate) first missions walktrough on device
snippet.description:
First missions of the Skyward Battles game for Playdate console. Walkthrough game missions on the device, let's see how it plays, game performance, and controls.
Review of the game on the Playdate Player channel 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mEeK6ynSgkU
The game was released on Itch. #SkywardBattles #playdate #crankworkgames #arcade #action #flying #gameplay #games #game #indiegame #1bit #8bit #retrogaming
